{"type":"message","id":"16132046","parentId":"5413da73","timestamp":"2026-06-24T14:55:48.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Oz5eMUnofiqGQmcCDkc94798","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"680:### `gateway.reload`\n685:    reload: {\n698:  - `\"hybrid\"` (default): try hot reload first; fall back to restart if required.\n700:- `deferralTimeoutMs`: optional maximum time in ms to wait for in-flight operations before forcing a restart or channel hot reload. Omit it to use the default bounded wait (`300000`); set `0` to wait indefinitely and log periodic still-pending warnings.\n834:- Injects live-reload client into served HTML.\n838:- Disable live reload for large directories or `EMFILE` errors.\n984:- Active-surface filtering applies during activation: unresolved refs on enabled surfaces fail startup/reload, while inactive surfaces are skipped with diagnostics."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":127,"aggregated":"680:### `gateway.reload`\n685:    reload: {\n698:  - `\"hybrid\"` (default): try hot reload first; fall back to restart if required.\n700:- `deferralTimeoutMs`: optional maximum time in ms to wait for in-flight operations before forcing a restart or channel hot reload. Omit it to use the default bounded wait (`300000`); set `0` to wait indefinitely and log periodic still-pending warnings.\n834:- Injects live-reload client into served HTML.\n838:- Disable live reload for large directories or `EMFILE` errors.\n984:- Active-surface filtering applies during activation: unresolved refs on enabled surfaces fail startup/reload, while inactive surfaces are skipped with diagnostics.","cwd":"/home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782312948822}}
