{"type":"message","id":"83c2649e","parentId":"68c46c5a","timestamp":"2026-06-24T14:55:53.362Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_lkjKPBbuHwX1EZaDH7zO4943","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"15:- `openclaw config schema` prints the live JSON Schema used for validation and Control UI, with bundled/plugin/channel metadata merged in when available\n16:- `config.schema.lookup` returns one path-scoped schema node for drill-down tooling\n19:Agent lookup path: use the `gateway` tool action `config.schema.lookup` for\n1271:Current builds no longer include the TCP bridge. Nodes connect over the Gateway WebSocket. `bridge.*` keys are no longer part of the config schema (validation fails until removed; `openclaw doctor --fix` can strip unknown keys)."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":125,"aggregated":"15:- `openclaw config schema` prints the live JSON Schema used for validation and Control UI, with bundled/plugin/channel metadata merged in when available\n16:- `config.schema.lookup` returns one path-scoped schema node for drill-down tooling\n19:Agent lookup path: use the `gateway` tool action `config.schema.lookup` for\n1271:Current builds no longer include the TCP bridge. Nodes connect over the Gateway WebSocket. `bridge.*` keys are no longer part of the config schema (validation fails until removed; `openclaw doctor --fix` can strip unknown keys).","cwd":"/home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782312953356}}
