{"type":"message","id":"237fa8d9","parentId":"4dc281e6","timestamp":"2026-06-24T15:28:51.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **big-pickel5** is live! Here's your full arsenal now:\n\n| Provider | Status |\n|---|---|\n| `9router/oc/big-pickle` | Default |\n| `big-pickel1/big-pickle` | ✅ Tested |\n| `big-pickel2/big-pickle` | ✅ Tested |\n| `big-pickel3/big-pickle` | ✅ Added |\n| `big-pickel4/big-pickle` | ✅ Added |\n| `big-pickel5/big-pickle` | ✅ Added |\n\nAll five OpenCode Zen fallbacks are configured, hot-reloaded, and pushed to the repo. Ready for whatever's next!"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"9router","model":"oc/big-pickle","usage":{"input":2108,"output":148,"cacheRead":83200,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":85456,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782314928241,"responseId":"8ba47c9e-0b32-47ea-b6d7-29dec3fb684c"}}
