{"type":"message","id":"2753e51a","parentId":"b17a28b9","timestamp":"2026-06-24T15:42:40.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All pushed! Here's what you've got now:\n\n### ✅ Setup & Start Scripts\n\n**`setup.sh`** — for a brand new codespace:\n1. Checks prerequisites (Node.js, npm, Git)\n2. Installs/updates `openclaw` and `9router` globally\n3. Copies `openclaw-config.json` into place (with all 5 big-pickel providers)\n4. Installs Tailscale + authenticates\n5. Makes all scripts executable\n6. Verifies everything\n\n**`start.sh`** — for restarting an existing codespace:\nRuns all 3 services in order:\n1. 🔗 `bin/start-tailscale` — starts tailscaled + connects\n2. 🌐 `bin/start-9router` — starts 9-router on port 20128\n3. 🤖 `bin/start-openclaw` — starts OpenClaw Gateway on port 18789\n\nWhen you grab that README and want to set up the remote browser and other stuff, we'll add those in later."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"9router","model":"oc/big-pickle","usage":{"input":2231,"output":271,"cacheRead":113792,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":45,"totalTokens":116294,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782315596915,"responseId":"65c5287d-08e7-4cbc-bdd1-0c738c64143c"}}
