{"type":"message","id":"d8718de9","parentId":"6e155e9c","timestamp":"2026-06-24T15:50:18.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pushed! ✅ Here's what's in the updated README:\n\n**Session continuity** — when you stop and restart the same Codespace, the Gateway saves session state to disk at `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json`. Since the codespace disk persists between stop/start, running `./start.sh` brings you right back where you left off — conversations, identity, everything. No extra steps needed.\n\n**README now covers:**\n- **Fresh codespace:** `git clone` → `./setup.sh` → `./start.sh`\n- **Same codespace restart:** just `./start.sh`\n- All 5 Big Pickel providers documented\n- Service overview diagram\n- Ports table (18789, 20128)\n- Troubleshooting section\n\nYou're good to go, Leon. Whenever you want to add the remote browser and Money Printer later, we can update everything then."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"9router","model":"oc/big-pickle","usage":{"input":2136,"output":209,"cacheRead":75648,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":19,"totalTokens":77993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782316214848,"responseId":"5747e5eb-8714-484a-9fae-032fba22cfbd"}}
