{"type":"message","id":"0a2a4958","parentId":"c9073a9a","timestamp":"2026-06-24T15:54:43.488Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Since the other files got deleted and I did not back them up anywhere, I want you to create a new branch on this same repository. \n\nPlease create a branch called \"main-backup.\" Whenever we push changes to the main branch, I want to be able to pull those changes into the \"main-backup\" branch myself. They shouldn't be added there automatically; I will be the one who manually pulls them to the \"main-backup\" branch.","timestamp":1782316481624,"idempotencyKey":"c04d8c0b-731c-49f5-9614-10c2231ddae5:user"}}
