{"type":"message","id":"4f26121e","parentId":"7c3bfc55","timestamp":"2026-06-24T15:54:50.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! ✅ Branch **`main-backup`** has been created off the current `main` state and pushed to the repo.\n\nIt's a static snapshot right now — whatever you push to `main` going forward won't touch it. When you want to sync, you just:\n\n```bash\ngit checkout main-backup\ngit pull origin main\ngit push origin main-backup\n```\n\nWhenever you're ready to start adding the remote browser and Money Printer, I'm here."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"9router","model":"oc/big-pickle","usage":{"input":2130,"output":103,"cacheRead":75392,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":4,"totalTokens":77625,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782316487463,"responseId":"a135d654-3753-4378-97ef-cb5ef840ed12"}}
